[SN]TITLE[SN]
Ugly animals need more public attention to survive

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
We often hear about animals that are endangered or facing extinction.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
28 March 2016 Last updated at 08:20 BST
But have you noticed how most of those animals are cute ones? What about the not-so-cute animals?
Well a study has found that ugly animals are struggling to get the same attention.
